				ABOUT US
			</h1>
			<p class="w-[100%] mt-[5vh]">
				Streetlight Studio's team is built of 18 employees with diverse backgrounds, all of which have decades worth of development experience in entertainment and technology. from our emmy award winning producers, to our developers with decades of programming and development, we've come together to disrupt the games and entertainment industry. by providing an agile footprint with cost-effective measures, we can circumvent the massive overspending that has plagued the games industry and bring the dreams of clients to life. streetlight studios is proudly owned entirely by people of color.
			</p>
