			<h1 class="text-[#FFED68] text-center tracking-normal font-[Dosis] font-extrabold text-[36px] md:text-[80px] lg:text-[120px] leading-[1] pt-[20vh] opacity-100 mb-10">CAMPAIGN</h1>
