				<Image src={campaignPreview} alt="Streetlight Studios" class="bg-white shadow-[inset_0px_3px_6px_#00000029] border-[10px] border-[#FFED68] rounded-[2rem] opacity-100 mx-8"/>
				<div id="campaign-desc" class="!w-fit flex flex-col gap-y-8">
					<p>Calling all adventurers! Streetlight Studio has just unveiled their upcoming project, and it’s set to take the roleplaying game world by storm. Moondrift Memory, a new CRPG utilizing the Pathfinder Second Edition System, is officially in development and it’s bringing some serious star power along for the journey. Powered by the new cuttingedge Starstone Engine, this game isn’t just for Pathfinder veterans—it’s for everyone who’s ever dreamed of forging their own legendary tale. The first chapter of the game, MoondriftMemory: Prologue, is launching on Kickstarter on March 18, 2025!</p>
					<p>Joining the talented team is legendary voice actor Sean Schemmel (Dragon Ball Z, Dragon Ball Daima, Pokémon). Schemmel is bringing his expertise to the project as both talent and Voice Director. Voice Actor Alejandra Reynoso (Pokemon Horizons, Casltevania, Winx Club) brings her talent as a voice actor onto the team. Pathfinder legend Tan Shao Han (Pathfinder: Secrets of Magic, Pathfinder: Rival Academies, Pathfinder: Impossible Lands, Pathfinder Adventure Path: Let the Leaves Fall) has joined the writing team as well, crafting an unforgettable narrative for the game. Streetlight Studio has more exciting talent attached to the project and will be announcing them in March during their campaign launch.</p>
					<p>Designed as a top-down isometric CRPG, Moondrift Memory is an immersive experience tailored for both die-hard Pathfinder fans and those just beginning their tabletop journey. Players will lead a party of up to four adventurers through the dark, frigid valley of Moondrift, venturing deep into the ruins of a dragon’s lair. This introductory chapter masterfully teaches the core mechanics of Pathfinder Second Edition, covering combat, exploration, downtime, and social encounters—one thrilling moment at a time.</p>
				</div>
